      .section
        h3.section-title Privacy Policy for PensNews
        p At PensNews, accessible from Dapur Rakyat News, one of our main priorities is the privacy of our visitors. This Privacy Policy document contains types of information that is collected and recorded by Limasdiet and how we use it.
